    <article id="post-9408" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/9408.html" rel="bookmark">基于 Laravel + Pusher + Vue 通过事件广播构建实时聊天室应用</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-05-25T10:08:52+08:00">2018-05-25</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2018-05-25T23:12:40+08:00">2018-05-25 23:12:40</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    11115 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../post/9408.html#comments">
                        27 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9408.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/livechat-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9408.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="820" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/livechat-820x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>
前言：学院君之前有说过要整理出一篇事件广播手把手教程，今天终于兑现了，本教程基于 Laravel + Pusher + Vue，以事件广播作为核心技术，从零开始让你在几分钟内即可搭建起一个实时聊天室应用。不多废话，直接上手吧。
应用初始化
安装配置
首先还是通过 Composer 安装一个全新的聊天室应用：
 composer create-project laravel/l...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <footer class="entry-meta">
            <p class="visible-xs">
                <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9408.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
